```xml
<odoo>
    <data>
        <record id="prevent_sales_zero_priced_products_view_form" model="ir.ui.view">
            <field name="name">prevent.sales.zero.priced.products.form</field>
            <field name="model">product.template</field>
            <field name="arch" type="xml">
                <form string="Product">
                    <header>
                        <button name="action_prevent_sales_zero_priced_products" type="object" string="Prevent Sales" class="oe_highlight" attrs="{'invisible': [('list_price', '!=', 0)]}"/>
                    </header>
                    <sheet>
                        <div class="oe_title">
                            <label for="name" class="oe_edit_only"/>
                            <h1>
                                <field name="name"/>
                            </h1>
                        </div>
                        <group>
                            <group>
                                <field name="list_price"/>
                            </group>
                        </group>
                    </sheet>
                </form>
            </field>
        </record>
    </data>
</odoo>
```
This XML file defines a form view for the `product.template` model. It adds a button in the header of the form view that is only visible when the `list_price` field is not equal to zero. When clicked, this button triggers the `action_prevent_sales_zero_priced_products` method on the `product.template` model.